* [[Tropical Storm Bonnie (2004)|Bonnie]]
* [[Hurricane Charley|Charley]]
* [[Hurricane Danielle (2004)|Danielle]]
* [[Tropical Storm Earl (2004)|Earl]]
* [[Hurricane Frances|Frances]]
* [[Hurricane Gaston (2004)|Gaston]]
|
* [[Tropical Storm Hermine (2004)|Hermine]]
* [[Hurricane Ivan|Ivan]]
* [[Hurricane Jeanne|Jeanne]]
* [[Hurricane Karl (2004)|Karl]]
* [[Hurricane Lisa (2004)|Lisa]]
* [[Tropical Storm Matthew (2004)|Matthew]]
* [[Subtropical Storm Nicole (2004)|Nicole]]
|
* [[Tropical Storm Otto (2004)|Otto]]
